pped if not supported by a physics engine, while required features prevent the engine from being loaded.\r\n\r\nPull request #573 started work on this but couldn't be merged in time for GitHub migration. We'll reopen the PR there.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>Currently, all features used by the physics system are required to load a physics engine. In the interest of supporting multiple physics engines with different sets of features, the physics system can be refactored so that some features are optional. Optional features are just skipped if not supported by a physics engine, while required features prevent the engine from being loaded.</p>\n<p><a href=\"#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-gazebo/pull-requests/573/optional-physics-features\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"ap-connect-link\">Pull request #573</a> started work on this but couldn't be merged in time for GitHub migration. We'll reopen the PR there.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "assignee": {"display_name": "Louise Poubel", "uuid": "{5cfa2075-477b-4ded-bdb9-8d2479544ec4}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B5cfa2075-477b-4ded-bdb9-8d2479544ec4%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B5cfa2075-477b-4ded-bdb9-8d2479544ec4%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/557058:6ff86fcb-b7ab-44a5-b8a6-f6d9cae8b6e8/7d903d90-c5ea-4182-b7ef-0d467e9e1c74/128"}}, "nickname": "chapulina", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:6ff86fcb-b7ab-44a5-b8a6-f6d9cae8b6e8"}, "state": "new", "version": null, "edited_on": null, "created_on": "2020-04-14T18:46:48.448880+00:00", "milestone": null, "updated_on": "2020-04-14T18:46:48.448880+00:00", "type": "issue", "id": 58}